🌐 Common Mistakes (VERY IMPORTANT 🚨)
❌ Mistake 1

“TCP is always better”

✔ Correct: Depends on use case

❌ Mistake 2

“IP identifies everything”

✔ Correct: Port identifies application

❌ Mistake 3

“DNS works locally only”

✔ Correct: DNS works globally

❌ Mistake 4

“HTTPS is a different protocol”

✔ Correct: HTTP + encryption

❌ Mistake 5

“MAC address works on internet”

✔ Correct: Only works in LAN

