🎯 10 Most Asked Computer Network Interview Questions (FINAL REVISION)
1️⃣ What is OSI model?

7-layer communication model.

2️⃣ What is TCP/IP model?

4-layer practical model.

3️⃣ What is DNS?

Name → IP converter.

4️⃣ What is NAT?

Private → public IP mapping.

5️⃣ What is HTTP?

Web communication protocol.

6️⃣ What is HTTPS?

Secure HTTP using encryption.

7️⃣ What is routing?

Path selection for data.

8️⃣ What is a port?

Application identifier.

9️⃣ What is firewall?

Traffic filtering system.

🔟 What is subnetting?

Dividing network into smaller parts.

